{
  "info": {
    "name": "MoneyBox API",
    "description": "Complete API collection for MoneyBox — a money collection tracking app with tab-scoped authentication isolation.\n\n## Tab Isolation Strategy\n\nThis app uses server-side sessions keyed by a unique tab identifier (`X-Tab-Id` header) instead of browser cookies. Each browser tab generates a unique ID stored in `sessionStorage` and sends it with every request via a global `fetch()` override.\n\n**Key concepts for testing:**\n- Each `X-Tab-Id` value represents an independent \"browser tab\"\n- Tab A and Tab B can be logged in as different users simultaneously\n- Logging out from one tab does NOT affect other tabs\n- Omitting the header equals a fresh, unauthenticated tab\n\n## Real Database Users\n\nThese users exist in the default database:\n- `admin_a@test.com` / `admin123` (admin)\n- `admin_b@test.com` / `admin456` (admin)\n- `usera@test.com` / `pass123` (regular user)\n- `dilshan.thalagahapitiya111@gmail.com` / `1234567890` (admin)\n\n## Collection Structure\n\n1. **🔐 Authentication** — Signup, Login, Logout, Session check\n2. **👤 Profile** — Profile picture management\n3. **📊 Collection** — Grid data, selections, partial payments\n4. **🎨 Color Rules** — Manage color ranges\n5. **🛡️ Admin** — User management + Export/Import DB\n6. **🔁 Tab Isolation Tests** — Multi-tab scenario tests",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
    "_exporter_id": "moneybox"
  },
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "🔐 Authentication",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Create User Account (Signup)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test(\"Account created successfully\", function () {",
                  "    const jsonData = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.expect(jsonData.ok).to.be.true;",
                  "    pm.expect(jsonData.message).to.include('created');",
                  "});"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              },
              {
                "key": "X-Tab-Id",
                "value": "{{tab_a_id}}"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n    \"name\": \"{{user_name}}\",\n    \"email\": \"{{user_email}}\",\n    \"password\": \"{{user_password}}\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/auth/signup",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "auth", "signup"]
            },
            "description": "Creates a new user account (requires admin approval before login)."
          }
